1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**

   The structure is composed of 10 blocks.  There are 5 layers.  The blocks are arranged in a somewhat  symmetrical, vertical design.  There is a central, vertical, orange cylinder block (10) supported by a base of light green rectangular block (5).  A yellow rectangular block (7) and two green rectangular blocks (3) form a square frame around a space above the orange cylinder.  A blue square block (1) sits on top of the green frame.  A small, reddish-orange triangular block (14) sits on top of the yellow rectangular block.

   * **Block Indices:** 5, 10, 7, 3, 3, 1, 14
